overview: This energetic collection captures a selection of hot Latin bands performing a vibrant assortment of songs. Featured artists Super Express, Exitos Durangenses, Xavier Passos and others deliver crowd-pleasing hits such as "El Pasadiscos," "Gritar Mi Dolor," "Agua Loca," "Hoy Empieza Mi Tristeza," "Cumbia del Sol" and "Rodeo."
title: 15 Exitos Agarron Musicalisimo Vol. 1
